Steps to Reproduce:

1.输入以下代码：
`
function timeout(ms){
return new Promise((resolve,reject)=>{
    setTimeout(resolve,ms);
})
}
async function asyncPrint(value,ms){
for(let i = 0; i< 5;i++){
     console.log(timeout(1500));
}
console.log(value);
}

asyncPrint('hello world',500);
`
2.多次点击自带的调试按钮会出现不一样的结果
